            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Preparing for Range Day: Using Arsenal Vault to Track Your Loadout</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">A smoother morning starts with knowing exactly what you're bringing and what ammo you need. Here's how to prep.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
